    <!-- Application Structure Plan: The SPA is structured as a thematic, interactive dashboard rather than a linear resume. This design tells a story of strategic growth. Key sections include a "Pillars of Impact" area with interactive case studies, a clickable career timeline, and a dedicated "Vision" section. This structure was chosen to highlight leadership and strategic thinking over chronological tasks, making it more engaging for a senior-level hiring manager and better showcasing the transition from "do-er" to "strategic leader." The new AI Chatbot provides an additional interactive layer for direct querying of the profile content. -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: Data is presented through interactive elements to enhance engagement. Key Stats (Inform) -> Dynamic number counters. YoY Growth (Compare) -> Chart.js bar chart for clear visual impact. Career Progression (Change/Organize) -> Clickable vertical timeline. Projects (Organize/Inform) -> Interactive cards revealing case studies (Challenge/Action/Result). The AI Chatbot (Inform/Engage) -> LLM-powered Q&A based on profile content. This approach breaks down complex achievements into digestible, interactive narratives, supporting the overall goal of demonstrating strategic leadership. Confirmed NO SVG/Mermaid. -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
